ResponseRule.name: Get Player's Attention--Initial Shout
ResponseRule.description: When player is close enough, Aaron shouts thru the glass trying to get the player to come closer.

ResponseRule.name: Get Player's Attention--My Name Is Aaron
ResponseRule.description: As the player comes into the room, Aaron introduces himself.

ResponseRule.name: Get Player's Attention--Loiter Lines
ResponseRule.description: When player is close enough, Aaron shouts thru the glass trying to get the player to come closer. Keeps shouting.

ResponseRule.name: Let Me Out of Here
ResponseRule.description: When player approaches glass, Aaron begs to be set free.

ResponseRule.name: Let Me Out of Here -- Already Raided Armory
ResponseRule.description: When player approaches glass, Aaron begs to be set free. In this case he has nothing to offer the player, just begging for his life.

ResponseRule.name: Loiter, Pleading Lines
ResponseRule.description: After initial request, Aaron keeps pestering to be let out.

ResponseRule.name: Player Saw Ingram's Rap Sheet
ResponseRule.description: After initial request, Aaron keeps pestering to be let out. Now starts commenting on the fact that the player saw his rap sheet.

ResponseRule.name: Loiter Version of Player Saw Ingram's Rap Sheet
ResponseRule.description: Altversion of convo if triggering via script doesn't work.

ResponseRule.name: Loiter, Pleading Lines After Rap Sheet
ResponseRule.description: Aaron reacts to the player having read his rap sheet.

ResponseRule.name: Player Started Mimic Extraction from Containment
ResponseRule.description: Prisoner reacts to seeing the player open the containment shield where the aliens area.

ResponseRule.name: Mimic Loaded Into Tube Done--UNUSED
ResponseRule.description: Prisoner reacts to seeing the telepath create a phantom out of husk.

ResponseRule.name: Pleading Lines -- Mimic Waiting in Tube, Loiter
ResponseRule.description: After telepath created a phantom. Aaron is starting to lose it.

ResponseRule.name: Player Released Mimic Chamber With Prisoner
ResponseRule.description: Player released a Phantom from the test chamber into the room with the prisoner. Prisoner Aaron curses the player before dying.

ResponseRule.name: Player Opened Mimic Chamber, Prisoner Free
ResponseRule.description: Prisoner reacts to the player opening live exam. Assumes the phantom isn't also alive trying to kill him.

ResponseRule.name: Thanks for Letting Me Out
ResponseRule.description: Aaron approaches player or vice versa after he's set free.

ResponseRule.name: ClickMe - Thanks for Letting Me Out
ResponseRule.description: Aaron approaches player or vice versa after he's set free.

ResponseRule.name: Raiding the Armory
ResponseRule.description: Prison and Player are in the armory together. Prisoner grabs a pistol.

ResponseRule.name: ClickMe, PrisonerAfter Freed Part 1
ResponseRule.description: Prisoner is out, standing around.

ResponseRule.name: ClickMe, Prisoner After Freed Part 2
ResponseRule.description: Prisoner is out, standing around.

ResponseRule.name: ClickMe, Prisoner After Freed Part 3 Optional (Rapsheet)
ResponseRule.description: Prisoner is out, standing around. Comments about the fact that you read his rapsheet after freeing him.

ResponseRule.name: Loiter, Prisoner After Freed Part 3
ResponseRule.description: Prisoner is out, standing around.

ResponseRule.name: ClickMe, Ingram In Shuttle Bay
ResponseRule.description: Prisoner is out, standing around.
